oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Jean Shepard at Hillbilly Heaven (flyer)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Shepard, Jean, 1933-2016; Metal photoplates;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: One color flyer (black on white) announcing Jean Shepard at the Hillbilly Heaven Night Club on April 28. Flyer features a metal photoplate of Jean Shepard and was printed for job no. 1041.
